snippet.title: Jerry Miculek - Pro Shooter
snippet.description:
Fast shooting? Check! SlowMo? Check! Comedy? Check! What more could you POSSIBLY want from a firearms channel!?
Jerry Miculek is arguably the fastest & most renown shooter to ever live. 

Now, the Miculeks as a family are bringing you unparalleled quality videos for the purpose of the education & fun of firearms!
